2.21	Ng_Man_Tat	Ng Man-tat	Ng Man Tat (traditional Chinese: ; simplified Chinese: ; Cantonese Yale: ng4 maang6 daat6) was born on 2 January 1952. He is a veteran actor in the Hong Kong film industry, with dozens of awards under his belt, including Best Supporting Actor at the 10th Hong Kong Film Awards for his role in A Moment of Romance.	
